# Assets Directory

This directory contains assets (images, diagrams, etc.) for blog posts.

## Directory Structure

```
posts/
├── your-post.md
├── another-post.md
└── assets/
    ├── rag-architecture.jpg
    ├── attention-diagram.png
    └── evaluation-metrics.svg
```

## Image Guidelines

- Use descriptive filenames
- Supported formats: JPG, PNG, SVG, WebP
- Optimize images for web (reasonable file sizes)
- Reference images in markdown using relative paths: `![Alt text](./assets/image.jpg)` 